
= example of Dutch [[Solar Energy Marketplaces]]

URL = https://vandebron.nl/

=Description=

"Vandebron arranges for consumers to buy electricity from independent producers. Based in the Netherlands, Vandebron, currently has 12 producers providing enough energy for 20,000 households. Customers receive their sustainable energy through the national grid, but from sources (typically farmers) and methodologies (wind, solar) selected by each individual customer. The company’s revenue stream is from subscriptions, which keeps them at arm’s length from promoting consumption." (http://www.web-strategist.com/blog/2015/04/23/how-the-collaborative-economy-is-impacting-the-energy-sector/)

